s-sociais/ciencias-politicas/comunicacion-y-poder-2967977?id_link=8787&amp;amp;adtype=pla&amp;amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMIvIKPodnx5QIVjYGRCh2p7AYgEAYYBSABEgIw9fD_BwE&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt; [9] As ruas e a Presidenta, Marcelo Branco, La Vanguardia dossier - &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
